id="iii.vii.xix-p21.1"></span>περὶ ἀποικίας</span>: *De Migratione
Abrahami.* Upon <span id="iii.vii.xix-p21.2"></span>[Gen. xii.
1-6](../../../bib/kjv/gen012.htm#001.md)<span
