<span id="iii.vii.xix-p22"></span> <span class="Greek"><span
id="iii.vii.xix-p22.1"></span>βιοῦ σοφοῦ τοῦ κατὰ δικαιοσύνην
τελειωθέντος, ἢ νόμων ἀγρ€φων</span>. (According to Schürer, <span
class="Greek"><span id="iii.vii.xix-p22.2"></span>δικαιοσύνην</span>
here is a mistake for <span class="Greek"><span
id="iii.vii.xix-p22.3"></span>διδασκαλίαν</span>, which is the true
reading in the original title.) This work, which is still extant, is
given by Mangey, II. 1–40, under the same title (<span
class="Greek"><span id="iii.vii.xix-p22.4"></span>διδασκαλίαν</span>,
however, instead of <span class="Greek"><span
