them, so that the life of Joseph (see below, note 26) in the <span
class="c13"><span id="iii.vii.xix-p22.8"></span>mss.</span> follows
directly upon that of Abraham (Schürer, p. 848 sqq.).

<span id="fn_434"></span>[120:435](2010060.htm#fr_434.md) <span
